{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-attribute-operator-blacklist/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-property-value-whitelist/","description":"declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations 限制一个单行声明块中声明的数量 选项 int：允许的最大声明数量。 例如，使用 1： 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规：","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations\"><a href=\"#declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations</h1>\n<p>限制一个单行声明块中声明的数量</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑            ↑\n * 这些声明的数量 */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>int</code>：允许的最大声明数量。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>1</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>,\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>,\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-block-single-line-max-declarations/index.html.a4d80447a186aa2d3d0e881074cdc5d9.json"}